<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2578:2601'>抵家以洪武五年壬子十有一月十二日卒年六十有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2601:2627'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '010-7a' );" name="010-7a" class="pb">[010-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
